      <div class="section-eyebrow">Our Story</div>
      <h2>Born from a <em>Passion</em><br/>for the Perfect Feast</h2>
      <p>Elamrit began with a simple but profound belief: that every meal served at a meaningful occasion deserves the same reverence as the occasion itself. Founded in Pune by a team of culinary artisans and event specialists, we started with a singular focus — to make luxury catering accessible to those who appreciate the extraordinary.</p>
      <blockquote>
        <p>"Elamrit crafts unforgettable culinary experiences, blending the richness of tradition with modern elegance."</p>
      </blockquote>
      <p>Over the years, our footprint has grown from intimate Pune celebrations to grand Pan India events — destination weddings in Rajasthan, corporate galas in Mumbai, anniversary feasts in Bangalore. Every event we touch carries the same DNA: meticulous preparation, seasonal ingredients, and service that anticipates before it responds.</p>
